ygData.msgSnippet: Yes, i went to qeynos and the guards judges me amiably. At lvl 29 get a partner to kill treant or go to highkeep and solo pickclaw lookout, very good exp and
ygData.messageBody:
Yes, i went to qeynos and the guards judges me amiably. At lvl 29 get a partner to kill treant or go to highkeep and solo pickclaw lookout,
very good exp and theres a safe spot there for you to run to when you get in trouble, No death.
